    "full-english": "My G-d, the soul which You have given in me pure it is. You created it, You formed it, You breathed it into me, and You preserve it. within me, and You will eventually take it from me, and to restore it to me in the time to come. So long as the soul is within me, thank I You, ETERNAL, my G-d and G-d of my ancestors, Master of all works. L-rd of all souls. Blessed You are ETERNAL, Who restores souls to bodies dead."
